data.name: Valkyrie Funfte
data.desc: "Valkyrie" monsters you control gain 200 ATK for each of your opponent's banished monsters. If you control a "Valkyrie" monster other than "Valkyrie Funfte": You can send 1 Spell/Trap from your Deck to the GY. You can only use this effect of "Valkyrie Funfte" once per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
